      <title>川普媒體股價上漲，因暗示“潛在的市場操縱”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/trump-media-shares-gain-it-alerts-nasdaq-potential-market-manipulation-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐納德·川普的媒體和科技公司的股價週五上漲超過 3%，此前該公司要求納斯達克交易所幫助防止所謂的「裸」賣空者操縱其股票的市場。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/trump-media-shares-gain-it-alerts-nasdaq-potential-market-manipulation-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 16:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
